OL,3,CMeet the seven-year-old litter picker
OL,4,Cwho's determined to keep his school
OL,5,Ctidy
OL,7,FReuben told ITV News' Ben McGrail he
OL,8,Fwanted to 'make the world a better
OL,9,Fplace'.
OL,11,FA 7 year-old boy from Taunton has said
OL,12,Fhe wants to 'make the world a better
OL,13,Fplace' by picking up litter and
OL,14,Fencouraging his friends to do the same.
OL,16,FReuben Norman has taken it upon
OL,17,Fhimself to do regular rubbish
OL,18,Fcollecting both at his school and in
OL,19,Fthe surrounding neighbourhood.
