OL,3,CMeet the seven-year-old litter picker
OL,4,Cwho's determined to keep his school
OL,5,Ctidy
OL,7,FAs well as the litter-picking, Reuben
OL,8,Fis also raising money to help buy new
OL,9,Fequipment for Minerva Primary School
OL,10,Fso his friends can join him.
OL,12,FHe said: "I want to make the world a
OL,13,Fbetter place. Every day when I bring
OL,14,Fmy litter-picking equipment I pick up
OL,15,Flitter on my way to school."
OL,17,FWhen asked why he does it, he said:
OL,18,F"Happy and sad that people litter."
