OL,3,CMeet the seven-year-old litter picker
OL,4,Cwho's determined to keep his school
OL,5,Ctidy
OL,7,FHis mum, Emily Howard, said: "We've
OL,8,Fbeen going out every day - after
OL,9,Fschool, on the weekends. We're very
OL,10,Fproud of him."
OL,12,FHead at Minerva Primary School, Gareth
OL,13,FNation, said: "He's an inspiration,
OL,14,FReuben's a real inspiration to others.
OL,15,FHe's an absolute delight, he's a role
OL,16,Fmodel pupil to others, he demonstrates
OL,17,Four values on a daily basis, which is
OL,18,Fwonderful."
